Nigerian fashion brand OUCH has unveiled its latest collection tagged The OUCHFARI.  According to the statement of the brand: The OUCHFARI is a perfect blend between the traditional kaftan and the formal English suit. An answer to an alternative for the man of style who is only presented with the option of a suit, blazer or kaftan. Made from the finest of 120s, 130s and 150 super Merino and Australian wool, The OUCHFari is presently available only as made-to-measure. See the full collection below.  Credits
